Subject to the terms of this Agreement and payment of all applicable fees, Licensor grants Licensee a **limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, non-sublicensable, revocable** license to:

**(a)** Install and operate the Software on the number of Devices specified in the purchased license tier.

**(b)** Use the Software solely for its intended purpose: malware detection, threat analysis, and security monitoring on systems owned by or under the direct management authority of Licensee.

**(c)** Use the SDK solely for building integrations between the Software and Licensee's own infrastructure. SDK usage does not grant any rights to distribute, resell, or sublicense the Software or any derivative thereof.

**(d)** Install and use Plugins exclusively in conjunction with a validly licensed instance of the Software.

