**(c)** Distribute, sublicense, lease, rent, loan, sell, resell, or otherwise transfer the Software, Detection Assets, or any rights therein to any third party, whether for commercial or non-commercial purposes.

**(d)** Remove, alter, obscure, or tamper with any proprietary notices, labels, trademarks, watermarks, or copyright markings embedded in or associated with the Software.

**(e)** Use the Software, SDK, Detection Assets, or any output thereof to develop, train, enhance, benchmark, or otherwise contribute to any product or service that competes with or substitutes for the Software.

**(f)** Use the Software in any manner that violates applicable local, national, or international laws or regulations, including but not limited to data protection laws.

**(g)** Share, publish, disclose, or transmit License Keys, authentication tokens, JWT credentials, device registration data, or any other access credentials to any unauthorized party.

**(h)** Circumvent, disable, interfere with, or attempt to bypass any license verification, authentication, tamper detection, or security mechanism in the Software.

**(i)** Use the Software on more Devices than permitted by the purchased license tier, or use a single License Key on multiple Devices unless explicitly authorized.

**(j)** Extract, export, copy, or redistribute Detection Assets independently from the Software, or use Detection Assets with any third-party scanning or analysis tool.

**(k)** Use the SDK to build products or services offered to third parties unless explicitly authorized in writing by Licensor.

**(l)** Perform or publish performance benchmarks, security assessments, or comparative analyses of the Software without prior written consent from Licensor.

