**(a)** Licensor reserves the right to audit Licensee's use of the Software to verify compliance with this Agreement.

**(b)** Audits may be conducted remotely through the Software's license verification and telemetry systems, or through written request for a self-certification by Licensee.

**(c)** If an audit reveals unauthorized use (including but not limited to excess Devices, unauthorized redistribution, or circumvention of license controls), Licensee shall promptly pay all applicable fees for such unauthorized use and reimburse Licensor's reasonable audit costs.

